<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Event Live Stream Started - FaNect</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 24px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .brand {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #16a34a  !important;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .title {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #111827;
      margin: 24px 0 8px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .content {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #374151;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .receipt-box {
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding: 16px;
      border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
    }

    .receipt-item {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
      margin-top: 32px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .email-container {
        padding: 16px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
      <a href="https://fanect.com" class="brand">FaNect</a>
    </div>

    <div class="title">ðŸ”´ Event Live Stream Started</div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi {{userName}},</p>

      <p>The live stream for your event has just started! Here are your event details:</p>

      <div class="receipt-box">
        <div class="receipt-item">
          <strong>Event:</strong>
          <span>{{eventName}}</span>
        </div>
         <div class="receipt-item">
          <strong>Event Date:</strong>
          <span>{{eventDate}}</span>
        </div>
         <div class="receipt-item">
          <strong>Event Time:</strong>
          <span>{{eventTime}}</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>You can now join the stream. For any assistance, kindly contact support@fanect.com.</p>

      <p>Enjoy the event!<br/>â€” The FaNect Team</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      &copy; {{year}} FaNect. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>